  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Ensure all fonts are imported properly (DM Sans).",
    "Apply precise hex codes exactly as specified in the component_styles and colors sections. The background MUST be #080c12.",
    "Apply linear gradients accurately to primary buttons.",
    "Implement the specific typography sizing and letter spacing down to the pixel for headers and labels.",
    "Maintain high density 'Control Room' bento grid layouts for the Dashboard.",
    "Ensure the sidebar width is exactly 220px, and the active nav item style matches exactly: border-left blue and linear gradient background.",
    "Do not use heavy borders on tables, use exact 1px #0f1520.",
    "Badge opacity must be 18% as requested.",
    "Add data-testid attributes to ALL interactive elements."
  ]
